Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This short kimono coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wow! This lining is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's the work of a genius painter who made a name for himself a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's someone cooking in the mountains here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sometimes when you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can see white smoke rising up in places.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's as if the smoke's wafting slowly\N upward from peoples' homes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:45.48,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,3170)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.59,0:00:45.48,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,1100)\be1}Clothes That Embrace the Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know, someone must be living up in those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? No one lives beyond here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I see lots of smoke rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then someone must be burning charcoal or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The mountain god is cooking his meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gods cook, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How else are they going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gods don't get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:25.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816.19,585.905)\fad(3000,3000)\p1\blur1\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\bord10\clip(675,530,957,642)\shad0}m 0 0 l 300 0 300 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:25.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814.857,585.906)\fad(3000,3000)}Mushishi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then he must be heating his bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Head on home now and cook our meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:27.86,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, there were mysterious\N things in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mountains look the same as they did then,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but they're no longer the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until that time, our hometown certainly felt as if it were wrapped in a soft cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis... what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it so that you can make yourself presentable to your art teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's woven from silk thread from\N silkworms from the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and dyed with plants found in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, if you can't return... that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you become successful, Father will forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at this sometimes, and think of home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will absolutely become a fine artist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I so wish I could start painting soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2185)\i1}I wonder how Sis and the others are doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinse those plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting warmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, give me a hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This lining... whose work is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,M-mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me! I wanted to paint so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You drew this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,From tomorrow, I want you in the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there isn't much I can teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no... I'm out of paint...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when I'm so close to finishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The delivery date is coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, don't worry, it'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now... what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There isn't anyone else I can borrow money from...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I have nothing left to sell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:50.87,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\pos(712.667,426.666)}Ho{\fs28.2}ck {\fs28.4}Sh{\fs28.6}op
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's badly tattered... I can't give you much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'll come right back to redeem it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why your master had such confidence in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To think someone with your talent is still an unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is short notice, but can you paint another one by next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandson's wedding is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll also be a good opportunity \Nto make a name for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By all means! Let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I have no time to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You work was tremendously popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got all these orders for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You did me proud. Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see... what shall I paint next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:08.82,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H8E8178\blur1\pos(780,228)\clip(m 726 202 l 726 202 706 259 686 243)}Hock Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:08.90,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H8E8178\blur1\pos(780,228)\clip(m 774 190 l 748 256 652 237 759 166 729 242)}Hock Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:08.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H8E8178\blur1\pos(780,228)\clip(m 688 200 l 788 197 770 246 814 201 788 264 673 250)}Hock Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:09.07,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H8E8178\blur1\pos(780,228)\clip(m 672 192 l 834 203 815 254 857 206 833 262 648 253)}Hock Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs44\c&H8E8178\blur1\pos(780,228)}Hock Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, here are today's letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just leave them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More deadline reminders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't they ever get tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Might as well save themselves the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I ever scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a huge landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that an entire village was swept away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was almost caught in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was out west, at the foothills \Nof Mt. something or other...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way it could be our village...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is no time to be worrying about other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is an important time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to make a bigger and bigger name for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed... you are indeed a master...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But... have you not been well, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:28.77,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The paintings I had seen you do before seemed so truly full of life, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I might be worrying about nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn... what's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to be fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your medicine and rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the rush? Your reputation is now solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, how're you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink this. It'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many years has it been \Nsince she left to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if she's doing well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if Father will forgive me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ten years have already passed since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's selfish of me to think of \Nthem only at times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I want to see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2727)\i1}I want to walk through the scent of my hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's there to be afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I see them, I'll be able to create\N good paintings once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever in heaven's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you get your sister's letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a terrible landslide...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The homes, the fields... just about \Neverything was swept away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We got together and asked her\N to write a letter to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,asking you to help the village \Nsince you became famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Father and Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was killed in the landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister also died after giving birth to this child the following year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this for your own good... Go back to town...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He was quite a popular artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, he suddenly vanished\N and never came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That painting alone would fetch a good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a thin cloth, but it's unusually heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It definitely smells of mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you could probably sell it for a good price to that doctor who likes rare goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this price sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You say it's caused no trouble so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but without knowing the true nature of this mushi, I can't ask for a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it at half price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You jest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably bought it for the price of a rag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure you could learn its true nature and resell it at a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to deal with troublesome mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No mushi-shi would fork over a \Nfortune for something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one more piece to the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They say these mountains are in the artist's hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that will help your investigation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At half price it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry to hear that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you must come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't paint anything anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I hold the brush, nothing inspires me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today again... the mountains look so foreign to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as I have become a stranger\Nto the people of my hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I should go to live somewhere unknown to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The taste of... homegrown...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't feel dizzy nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I have energy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Toyo... All by yourself today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just on my way over to deliver these.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your granny at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny turned cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do about the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She had relatives on her father's side, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They live far away, but let's have them take her in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me... Let me take her in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's developing slowly both mentally and physically...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't raise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I vow to raise her with all my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, don't send her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyo, hold this for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like that. Let me do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you're doing it, it'll topple right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Don't spill it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's already five, but she's still a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,These are for your niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll love these...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mountains are back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That smoke... what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was a goner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Never should've bought that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No one you need to worry about...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's gotten lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... my coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came looking for the mountains to learn the true nature of the mushi that live in this coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,851)}But something odd happened when \NI set foot on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! My pack is getting heavier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I finally managed to escape from the mud,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the mushi seemed to have left the coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The mushi in the coat were {\i1}ubusuna{\i0} native to this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ubu... suna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mud-like mushi unique to each region.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're like that only when they're in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Above ground, they take a smoke-like form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear there was a big landslide in this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1384)}A large number of {\i1}ubusuna{\i0}\N were probably also swept away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}ubusuna{\i0} then found this coat\N and made it their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, quite a huge number were living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They might've gathered since {\i1}ubusuna{\i0} can't survive outside their own region.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:19:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This fabric... it was woven from the\Nmaterials in this area, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... My older sister made it completely from things found on the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the time I left home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,wearing this reminded me of the scents and sounds of the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ubusuna{\i0} congregate at the scents of home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They exist in small amounts in all plants that grow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And by eating the plants, animals become hosts to the {\i1}ubusuna,{\i0} as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As ubiquitous as they are, these \Nmushi have very little influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and if the host leaves the region, \Nthey completely lose their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he returns to the region where he was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll try protecting him for life from other minor mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they have something to do with\N a child's slow development?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That might happen, if the child didn't get enough {\i1}ubusuna{\i0} during its weaning period.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was the case, now that a huge number of {\i1}ubusuna{\i0} have returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll probably gradually catch up \Nif you feed her plenty of local foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you don't need this coat anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you sell it back to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I was planning on selling it off no matter what, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! This coat means a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. But I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A coat in which {\i1}ubusuna{\i0} live?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... And once in a great while,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,smoke rises from the mountains in the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once in how long a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe about once every ten years or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's truly a rare occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... This painting is also quite a work of art...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the work of a mysterious artistic genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I can't wait for the smoke to appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since I almost got myself killed, \NI suppose I can be forgiven for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? On this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The exact same painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No paints?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I still have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You're good...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Toyo. They're our mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Paint some more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I will!
